		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "本單元認為你剛剛體驗到了愛。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_defect", "CHAR_defect_left", "MOOD_shocked"],
			"dialog"			: "所以那就是愛！",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "怪物與扎拉登之間互相遺忘的機制於本單元仍是未知的。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "但是，相較於活在對怪物們的恐懼之中，去愛那些健忘的怪物們算是更好的替代。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "|C3|建議:|C0|繼續去愛那些怪物們。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_defect", "CHAR_defect_left", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "這是個好主意。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "本單元在你的心中偵測到了部分特殊性質。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "你的愛之子彈屬於|C12||I12|虛空元素。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "然而，你的|C3|蓄力攻擊|C0|卻屬於|C11||I11|光耀元素。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "所有怪物對特定的|C3|愛之元素|C0|都有著對應的弱點與抗性。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "|C3|舉例:|C0|大部分|C3|維目爾|C0|怪物對|C12||I12|虛空之愛|C0|存在抗性，然而她們更容易受到|C11||I11|光耀之愛|C0|的傷害。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "甚至在能量耗盡時，你的|C3|蓄力攻擊|C0|在這種情況下可能會更有效。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_bot", "CHAR_tutor_right", "MOOD_normal"],
			"dialog"			: "|C3|建議：|C0|使用合適的能力更有效地去愛怪物們。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_defect", "CHAR_defect_left", "MOOD_happy"],
			"dialog"			: "|wave|非常感謝你，愛的機器人。",
		},
		{
			"character"			: ["VOICE_defect", "CHAR_defect_left", "MOOD_awkward"],
			"dialog"			: "我一開始還有點害怕和你說話。",
